<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
    <title>After School</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/bootstrap-3.3.2-dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
        <br>
        <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
            <li role="presentation" class="active"><a href="#">오후 강좌</a></li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">강좌 삭제를 누르면 <strong>"<%=title%>"</strong>에 대한 모든 데이터가 <strong>"삭제"</strong> 됩니다.<br>이것은 매우 위험한 행동입니다.<br>관리자 또는 이 강좌의 강사가 아니라면 취소버튼을 누르세요.</div>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">
           강좌삭제
        </button>
        <a class="btn btn-warning btn-lg" href="/lecture/<%=lid%>" role="button">취소</a>
        <!-- Modal -->
        <div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="modal-dialog">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                        <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">강좌 삭제</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        마지막 경고입니다.<br>이 작업은 매우 위험합니다.<br>
                        정말로 이 <strong>"강좌(<%=title%>)"</strong> 를 삭제하시겠습니까?
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <a class="btn btn-default" href="/lecture/<%=lid%>" role="button">취소</a>
                        <a class="btn btn-danger" href="/deleteLecture/<%=lid%>" role="button">강좌삭제</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- jQuery (necessary for Bootstrap's JavaScript plugins) -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.2/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Include all compiled plugins (below), or include individual files as needed -->
    <script src="/bootstrap-3.3.2-dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
